        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center text-gradient">Featured Video</h2>
            <div class="featured-video-container">
                <div class="video-card featured">
                    <div class="video-wrapper">
                        <iframe
                            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kXivmHLYa3I?start=5"
                            title="Message of Hope"
                            frameborder="0"
                            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                            allowfullscreen
                        ></iframe>
                    </div>
                    <div class="video-info">
                        <h3>A Message of Hope and Healing</h3>
                        <p>An inspiring message about finding hope in times of darkness and the power of faith in mental health recovery.</p>
                        <div class="video-tags">
                            <span class="tag">Hope</span>
